public class ArbitraryTokenDomain
extends AbstractFiniteDomain

Artificial Intelligence A Modern Approach (3rd Edition): page 486. As in CSPs, domains can be sets of arbitrary tokens; we might choose the domain of Age to be {juvenile,teen,adult} and the domain of Weather might be {sunny,rain,cloudy,snow}.

Ciaran O'Reilly
